ScreenShot
===============================================
How to capture ScreenShot Using selenium
===============================================
To Capture Screenshot using Selenium webDriver type driver Object into takesScreenshot interface.
				((TakesScreenshot) driver)
Then we need to create call method as getScreenShotAS() here we need to pass one parameter.
OutputType.File
				((TakesScreenshot) driver).getScreenshotAs(OutputType.FILE);
				
After execution this statement selenium capture the ScreenShot store in a local memory.
If we want to move that screenshot local memory to our desired location, Then we need to call static method 
Copy(-,-).
Which is present in Filehandler class which accept two parameter path of source and path of destination.

Filehandler.copy(--,---); 




